infos.value: I'll protect you! I swear it!
My blade serves to protect Leonis. Right, Brother?
The Leonis line must live on, even should we fall afoul of gods to defend it.
The favor bestowed upon Hourne...
Hmph. Don't think that you can surpass me.
My mind was made up long ago.
What kind of weapon would you like me to make? Huh? You want me to fight?
I will lend you my power. But in exchange, you'll have to show me your resolve.
I have confidence in my white magic. Please make use of my talents.
Show me strength that can move even the most hardened of hearts.
Perhaps it would be best to demonstrate the pride of Leonis?
I'm not going to die yet. I'm doing this to live.
As ever the stars sparkle...
Let's see how far we can push this aging sword, shall we?
I shall show you...the strength of a true dragoon.
You want something from me, it's going to cost you. So pay up.
Don't you know that curiosity killed the cat?
No one who mocks me will be forgiven. No one!
Sister, you gave us the hope we needed to keep living!
Here comes the secret weapon!
For our comrades!
May the light of the Crystals guide you.
Witness the might of the First Sword of Hourne.
What is it people say...? Oh yeah! I'm all over it like a rash!
Ah... I sure am hungry...
I'll carve my name into their hearts!
Well, I suppose I can accompany you for a little bit.
It'll all work out somehow. For now, we need to move forward to do what we must.
Those who defy fate shall meet their end...
I won't miss! Probably.
I dislike the army, but I'm glad I can do some research.
May the light of the Crystals guide you.
I'd like to get a reward for proving myself in battle!
It's my purpose in life to take as many lives as possible.
Child of mortals. You put too much faith in your own abilities.
No matter where you decide to go, I will be there, guarding your back.
Bang, bang! One down!
Do you think anyone would shed a tear for me?
I'll make quick work of any enemy.
You probably shouldn't be asking me for directions. Tee hee!
I shall not sully the name of House Beoulve!
You wish to hire me? I should hope you have the coin.
The power of the Thunder God... You truly need it?
May the light of the Crystals guide you.
I'll keep supporting him from the shadows. That's enough for me.
Gracefully, elegantly... This dance will be your last!
I've no interest in weaklings.
I love nothing more than squashing and smashing all those needless feelings of love and whatnot people have for each other.
Shall I teach you why they call me the Vermilion Devil?
I simply despise being confined.
If only I could magic away everyone in the world...except for Brother, of course.
As a Knight of Grandshelt, I will not fail to protect you.
How do you do? Might someone fancy a quick bout?
No matter what happens... I have no regrets!
I will fight in order to protect those whom I love.

Is it the crystals that guide me here?
No matter, my strength shall be yours!
No matter who my opponent may be, my path is unwavering.
Allow me to show you the sword technique of the east.
Feast your eyes upon me, Oldoa of King Muraga's imperial guard!
I refuse to leave. No matter what happens, I shall not return.
Our lives are as fleeting as our dreams. What a somber thought.
Are you knights as well? So even here, I'm still a misfit...
Guns require no charge time. Simply aim and fire!
Giving up is not an option, for I am Queen Helena’s elite guard.
You can't escape your destiny!
I will wield this sword whenever my comrades are in need of it.
With this, everything is now in motion...
My Gouga...will be different.
Grrr! Only tricks and no treats!
Let me hear you scream!
Let's just say...I am a handsome wanderer.
I will fulfill my duties as chief. Now...come.
The people of Saiga are pitifully naive.
It's so hot out. Is everyone having a good time?
I wonder if a prince will come visit me once I'm an adult, too.
This is the end for you—not us!
I won't be a burden. I am a white mage, after all.
Then you've nothing to fear.
Oops...you saw me. Is it bad if a shinobi can't swim?
It is rather cold...but it is still a nice night.
Why must I impart happiness unto others?
If something is going to happen, I'm coming along, too!
Brother, I'll have you know I'm fully opposed to this.
My blade is one of darkness... If you have no qualms, I will gladly fight by your side.
...Get out of my sight. I’m not interested in weaklings.
I see straight through your schemes.
I won't use this power to fight, but to protect you all.
Give yourself up!
«Crucium», move out!
If danger closes in, run away without hesitating. That is an order from me.
It is time for the party. Let us enjoy it.
A present for me? You certainly have a lot of free time.
...Toy?
The curse of my people's history ends this day...
What's the matter? Is your little play-acting over already?
This is my story!
Right! Now, let's see what you can do!
Now is the time to shape your stories!
YoRHa unit 2B. Proceeding with mission.
Scanner models are good at hacking. I've always got your back.
I shall bear all responsibility. And I will live.
We are «Lumen», Your Highness's personal guard.
My husband or perhaps my sons, surely they would...
These are just leftovers from the ones I made for my brother.
I'll let you choose. Either take my hand...or die by it.
There's a new boss in town—an unkillable one...!
I am not driven by fleeting emotions.
We are human, after all, with all the thoughts and feelings that go with it.
Th' true pleasure o' battle lies in death throes an' bloodbaths.
As a Knight of Grandshelt, I shall protect everyone!
I will accept anything.
What a beautiful beach. Maybe it's time for a little break.
I don't hate the beach. Floating back and forth on the swimming tube...
Succeeding my father is not the only path forward for a swordmaker.
Ex-SOLDIER, you mean. And I don't work for free.
No more games─it's over!
Here. This is for you. The price depends on the customer.
I'm here for you! To help take the load off your shoulders! Whatever your problem, I got you.
May you continue to watch over me in times to come.
I make my own luck!
I am Elena. Warrior of the Azure Crystal, here to bathe this world in light.
Brother...
You should feel honored. You are now part of the next chapter of my great story.
There will always be someone stronger out there. You'd do well to remember that.
Happy Halloween! Let's make the most of it!
You do realize we're about to kill you, don't you?
I wish to see him in his glory as the one true ruler of Ardra.
What point would there be in questioning the right or wrong of the bloodshed?
She won't have to wait much longer—we'll be together soon.
Every day's fun. Even when we almost get ourselves killed.
Actually, I wondered... Might I...join you?
Quittin' time. Sorry, but this girl doesn't work after hours.
You have my word... We will protect your world.
Humans are curious creatures. I cannot comprehend them.
Gaze upon true terror!
Happy New Year. May another year of peace be upon us.
Happy holidays! This...is something I could get used to.
You want my power? Then kneel before me, puny mortal! I jest, hehe.
Mine is the arrow of justice, and with it I'll mend your wicked ways!
Suffer if you must, but never abandon your resolve.
I'll fight! I'll make this world a place where life can flourish.
A "thief"? I prefer the term "treasure hunter"!
I'm a soldier, not some love-starved twit!
Well then! I leave the rest in your capable hands! Show me what you can do, new recruit!
Was it you who summoned me? Well, can you keep up?
The name's Joker. I'll be taking that heart of yours...
It's me, Fist of the Phantom Star—I mean, Queen!
You can call me Violet. But remember everyone, that's "Violet," not "Violent."
My name is Astrius, liberator of the Crystals.
Resnick, third general of the Six Fangs of Heindler.
I'll teach you to show me some respect!
What IS this feeling? Perhaps I should write a letter.
May the light of the Crystals guide you.
May the light of the Crystals guide you.
They shall not go unavenged, I swear it.
They shall not go unavenged, I swear it.
I will eliminate all who stand in Lady Melnia's way.
There may be something far more sinister afoot than I had feared...
With my power, even the impossible is possible.
Today, we hit the beach. Go change into your swimwear!
I shall not sully the name of House Beoulve!
What kind of weapon would you like me to make? Huh? You want me to fight?
I shall show you...the strength of a true dragoon.
I dislike the army, but I'm glad I can do some research.
